content: Anyone else loving the spat between @realDonaldTrump and @DRUDGE? It’s nice to see the conservative Drudge Report no longer drinks the #MAGA Kool-Aid. #drudgereport #POTUS

We all collected signatures in March. What @hiral4congress did wrong was make a big deal about stopping public activities and announced they were ending canvasses — without following through. It’s a rookie move for a 3-time candidate. #peopleoverpolitics
